text: Gottlieb Neumair (born 14 November 1939) is a German wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman featherweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Living people Category:German male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of the United Team of Germany Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Munich
